      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.0JZU0FVnvAJ08fVR]{Paradigm Shift}</p>\n<p>Like a living grappling hook, your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.s9yQSGGO40x7tEM1]{Infinity Lash (Su)} helps you vault and scale obstacles. While wielding your infinity lash, you can use your Charisma modifier in place of your Strength modifier to calculate your Athletics modifier to climb and jump. While your infinity lash is empowered by one of your expended spell slots, you also gain a +5-foot enhancement bonus to your base speed, and you gain a climb speed equal to half your base speed. If the expended spell slot is at least 4th level, the enhancement bonus to your base speed increases to +15 feet. You must have the infinity lash<sup>GM</sup> alternate class feature to choose this paradigm shift.</p>\n<p><em>Select and enable the appropriate bonus for the spell level used.</em></p>"
